mal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd015ca0c342b38601c3dfceb188e3cccca5785","tid":35692,"uid":63209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人駕駛列車為3卡車，1卡車可載約700人，繁忙時間3分鐘1班車，即每小時最多載約14,000人，日後乘客變多，最多只能加至2分鐘1班車，即繁忙時間每小時載到21,000人<br />\n<br />\n呢條數點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161212/56036671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161212%2F56036671&d=98m4kCksxFEIJSHFkFyK%2BnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b9e1f8f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161212%2F56036671&h=c788be67\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161212/56036671</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗱，無人駕駛列車每班有三卡車，因為要無人駕駛，需要用到特殊車頭，目前香港行走嘅鐵路並唔識調頭，所以兩邊都要有特殊車頭<br />\n所以三卡車得一卡載到客，而因為一卡車可載約700人，所以3分鐘一班嘅話，一小時有20班車載700人由站頭到站尾，期間冇人上車都冇人落車，所以每小時係載約14,000人<br />\n<br />\n-會考數學拎U"},{"pid":"22b76e74f306eca8eb62feeaac9fee1b777a09d8","tid":35692,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無人駕駛列車為3卡車，1<del>卡</del><span style=\"color: red;\">班</span>車可載約700人，繁忙時間3分鐘1班車，即每小時最多載約14,000人，日後乘客變多，最多只能加至2分鐘1班車，即繁忙時間每小時載到21,000人<br />\n<br />\n呢條數點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161212/56036671\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161212%2F56036671&d=98m4kCksxFEIJSHFkFyK%2BnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b9e1f8f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161212%2F56036671&h=c788be67\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161212/56036671</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"465